2. The 13th day of May is appointed as the day on which section 44 of the 
Planning and Development, Maritime and Valuation (Amendment) Act 2022 
(No. 29 of 2022) shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

10 May, 2024. 

DARRAGH O’BRIEN, 

Minister for Housing, Local Government and Heritage. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 17th May, 2024.
